WEBVTT

00:02.649 --> 00:05.182
Can you recommend anything fun to do at night here?

00:05.569 --> 00:06.269
Certainly,...

00:06.413 --> 00:10.098
...there is a great mariachi band playing right here at our hotel.

00:10.308 --> 00:12.176
Well, I saw them last night.

00:12.413 --> 00:13.306
I had a great time,...

00:13.427 --> 00:15.483
...but I'd like to do something different tonight.

00:15.741 --> 00:16.922
Okay, well,...

00:17.014 --> 00:20.903
...then how about going to a traditional Mayan Dance performance?

00:21.071 --> 00:24.083
Yes, that sounds perfect. Where can I see that?

00:24.607 --> 00:28.143
There is a theater downtown called the Teatro Indianismo.

00:28.303 --> 00:29.994
They have nightly performances.

00:30.254 --> 00:32.757
Great! What time does the show usually begin?

00:33.036 --> 00:34.810
It starts at 8 every night.

00:35.199 --> 00:36.590
Would you reserve a seat for me?

00:36.755 --> 00:38.179
Sure, no problem.

